obvious.jung.data
Class JungObviousForest

java.lang.Object
  obvious.jung.data.JungObviousForest
All Implemented Interfaces:
obvious.data.Data, obvious.data.Forest<obvious.data.Node,obvious.data.Edge>, obvious.data.Graph<obvious.data.Node,obvious.data.Edge>, obvious.util.Adaptable
public class JungObviousForest
extends java.lang.Object
implements obvious.data.Forest<obvious.data.Node,obvious.data.Edge>

Implementation of an Obvious Forest based on Jung toolkit. This implementation wraps an existing Jung Forest object. This class directly binds Jung and Obvious methods since those two toolkits share the same design for graphs, trees and forests.

Author:
Hemery
See Also:
Forest
